------------
Installation
------------

1. go to https://www.meteor.com/install, select OS instructions and install meteor
2. git clone this project
3. use terminal to navigate to the folder
4. run 'meteor' in the terminal window
5. App is ready to go :)



------------
Summary
------------
Frontend:
  - Created a connection to the Instagram API and searched for media using a user inputted tag and search start and end dates
  - Used two way data bindings to create a more responsive app
  - Simple design to navigate results
  - Retrieve collection of photos saved

Backend: 
  - Used HTTP GETS to retrieve instagram photos
  - Used Mongo collections to store data and used for creating DB local (cached) connections
  - Created functions to save photos to a collection and retrieve that collection later

  